</ul>
</li>
<li><i>Globalhead</i> (1992, paperback 1994); <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0553562819" class="internal">ISBN 0-553-56281-9</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Hackers_(anthology)#Our_Neural_Chernobyl" title="Hackers (anthology)">"Our Neural Chernobyl"</a></li>
